review_text: Very small with trails that are not maintained. But nice view of water and the 2 mountains railroad bridge. Also has view to new REM bridge being built. Lots of swamp area so be prepared for mosquitos when wet. Takes about 15 minutes to do the tour of trails.
Great place to walk dog and access to great water views.
